  "loadingOverlayStop": "Stop",
  "@loadingOverlayStop": { "description": "PR-7 — UI-critic deferred from PR-1. Scoped label for the abort button inside `ActiveWorkoutLoadingOverlay`. The generic `cancel` key reads as 'cancel my workout' in the finish/discard phase (the user just confirmed the destructive action; 'Cancel' on the spinner reads as undoing the entire workout). 'Stop' is unambiguous: it stops the in-flight save/discard request and restores the prior state. Scoped to this single call site — every other dialog and Material control still uses `cancel`." },
